SarawakID is an individual's single-sign-on identity that allows secure access to Sarawak Government digital services. It is your online identity for accessing various government services online. There are two versions: SarawakID for individual use and SarawakID Corp (SID Corp) for corporations. You can register for SarawakID through the Sarawak Government website or in person at a Service Sarawak Kiosk or Counter. Once registered, you can verify your account at a Service Sarawak Counter, Kiosk, or via eKYC online or through the eKYC Sarawak Gov Mobile App.
